g.text: Initialize a new django project using the falco project template.
This is a wrapper around the django-admin startproject command using my custom
project template at https://github.com/Tobi-De/falco. This cli also includes
some additional commands to make setting up a new project faster.
start-project Initialize a new django project the falco way.
crud Generate CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
htmx Download the latest version (if no version is
htmx-ext Download one of htmx extensions.
work Run your whole django projects in one command.
sync-dotenv Synchronize the .env file with the .env.template
rm-migrations Remove all migrations for the specified
make-superuser Make a superuser from some pre-defined django
